%[text] ## Section 6: Summary
%[text] Here is a list of functions used in this tutorial.
%[text:table]
%[text] | Function | Purpose |
%[text] | --- | --- |
%[text] | `emk.mol.fromSmiles(smiles)` | Convert SMILES → Mol object |
%[text] | `emk.mol.toSmiles(mol)` | Convert Mol → canonical SMILES |
%[text] | `emk.mol.isValid(smiles)` | Check if SMILES is valid |
%[text] | `emk.viz.draw2d(mol)` | Draw 2D structural diagram in figure |
%[text:table]
%[text] 
